tle and benefits from the whole article width. To make them look even better, you can enable the <a href=\"?page_id=92\">Widgetkit Spotlight</a> effect on all Featured Images.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-auto\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/features_featured_image.jpg\" width=\"344\" height=\"250\" alt=\"Demo\" title=\"Featured Image Spotlight\" />\r\n  <figcaption>Featured Image Spotlight</figcaption>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li>\r\n    Joomla: Add an <em>Intro Image</em> to your article in the <em>Images and Links</em> option<br/>\r\n    WordPress: Click <em>Set featured image</em> in the post and upload the image you want to add\r\n  </li>\r\n   <li>\r\n    Joomla: Set the <em>Image Float</em> to <em>none</em><br/>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    Enable <em>Featured Spotlight</em> in the template configuration if you like<br/>\r\n  </li>\r\n</ol>','Featured Images','','publish','open','open','','featured-images','','','2013-01-09 10:36:36','2013-01-09 10:36:36','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=655',0,'post','',0),(659,1,'2012-12-20 11:56:51','2012-12-20 11:56:51','<p>Solar provides different style variations of the default theme. In addition to these styles we added several other style settings like colors and fonts. Combining the different style options allows you to create your own unique website design.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"size-auto\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/features_style_settings.png\" height=\"350\" width=\"660\" alt=\"Demo\" title=\"\" /></p>','Style Variations','','publish','open','open','','style-variations','','','2013-01-09 10:36:53','2013-01-09 10:36:53','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=659',0,'post','',0),(661,1,'2012-12-20 11:55:24','2012-12-20 11:55:24','<p>Customize your header as you like. Choose between different colors and combine them with cool textures.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<p><img class=\"size-auto\" src=\"wp-content/uploads/yootheme/features_style_settings.png\" height=\"350\" width=\"660\" alt=\"Demo\" title=\"\" /></p>','Header Backgrounds ','','publish','open','open','','header-backgrounds','','','2013-01-09 10:37:07','2013-01-09 10:37:07','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=661',0,'post','',0),(663,1,'2012-12-20 11:54:20','2012-12-20 11:54:20','<p>This theme comes with different module styles, badges and icons. For each module you can pick a style and combine it with an icon or badge to create your own unique look.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=39\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fixed Header & Menu</h2>\r\n<p>Enhance your website with an eyecathing header effect. Just set the header fixed to hide it with a cool scroll effect and the main menu fixed at the top of the site and fix the main menu at the top of the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Beautiful Typography</h2>\r\n<p>Solar offers some neat styles for all HTML elements and a great set of CSS classes as well as several different fonts you can choose from to style your content.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=35\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Responsive Layout</h2>\r\n<p>Of course Solar comes with a completely responsive design which adapts perfectly for all device resolutions.</p>\r\n  \r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Warp 6</h2>\r\n<p>Solar is based on the Warp6 them framework, which is a fast and slick theme framework built on the latest web techniques like HTML5, CSS3 and PHP 5.2+.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/themes/warp-framework\" target=\"_blank\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n','Module Styles','','publish','open','open','','module-styles','','','2013-01-09 10:37:26','2013-01-09 10:37:26','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=663',0,'post','',0),(665,1,'2012-12-20 11:53:23','2012-12-20 11:53:23','<p>Solar offers some neat styles for all HTML elements and a great set of CSS classes as well as several different fonts you can choose from to style your content.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=35\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Module Styles</h2>\r\n<p>This theme comes with different module styles, badges and icons. For each module you can pick a style and combine it with an icon or badge to create your own unique look.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=39\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fixed Header & Menu</h2>\r\n<p>Enhance your website with an eyecatching header effect. Just set the header fixed to hide it with a cool scroll effect. The main menu is attached to the top of the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n \r\n<h2>Responsive Layout</h2>\r\n<p>Of course Solar comes with a completely responsive design which adapts perfectly to all device resolutions.</p>\r\n  \r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Warp 6</h2>\r\n<p>Solar is based on the fast and slick Warp6 Theme Framework, which is built with the latest web techniques like HTML5, CSS3 and PHP 5.2+.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/themes/warp-framework\" target=\"_blank\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n','Beautiful Typography','','publish','open','open','','beautiful-typography','','','2013-01-09 10:38:41','2013-01-09 10:38:41','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=665',0,'post','',0),(668,1,'2012-12-20 11:52:27','2012-12-20 11:52:27','<p>We created a custom style for our <a href=\"?page_id=88\">Widgetkit Spotlight</a>, perfectly fitting the theme.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<h4>Slideshow</h4>\r\n<ol>\r\n  <li>Download and unzip the bonus styles package for Widgetkit available in the download area</li>\r\n  <li>Copy the folder <strong>slideshow/styles/solar</strong></li>\r\n  <li>\r\n    Joomla: Paste it to <strong>media/widgetkit/widgets/slideshow/styles</strong><br/>\r\n    WordPress: Paste it to <strong>wp-content/plugins/widgetkit/widgets/slideshow/styles</strong>\r\n  </li>\r\n  <li>Now you can select the style \"Solar\" in the settings of your Widgetkit Slideshow</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n','Custom Widgetkit Styles','','publish','open','open','','custom-widgetkit-styles','','','2012-12-20 12:49:54','2012-12-20 12:49:54','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=668',0,'post','',0),(671,1,'2012-12-20 11:51:38','2012-12-20 11:51:38','<p>As a little extra Solar theme offers a set of social icons. They are easy to add to your content and are part of our editable Adobe Fireworks Image Source Files.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"social-icons\">\r\n  <li class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"rss\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"facebook\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"flickr\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"xing\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"google-plus\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"youtube\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"vimeo\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"github\"><a href=\"#\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Here is a little code example how to add them:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;social-icons&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;twitter&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;rss&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;flickr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;xing&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;google-plus&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;youtube&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;vimeo&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;github&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Possible class names are <strong>twitter, rss, facebook, flickr, xing, google-plus, youtube, vimeo</strong> and <strong>github</strong>.</p>','Social Icons','','publish','open','open','','social-icons','','','2013-01-09 11:08:49','2013-01-09 11:08:49','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=671',0,'post','',0),(674,1,'2012-12-20 11:20:50','2012-12-20 11:20:50','<p>Of course Solar comes with a completely responsive design which adapts perfectly to all device resolutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Module Styles</h2>\r\n<p>This theme comes with different module styles, badges and icons. For each module you can pick a style and combine it with an icon or badge to create your own unique look.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=39\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fixed Header & Menu</h2>\r\n<p>Enhance your website with an eyecatching header effect. Just set the header fixed to hide it with a cool scroll effect. The main menu is attached to the top of the site.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=33\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Beautiful Typography</h2>\r\n<p>Solar offers some neat styles for all HTML elements and a great set of CSS classes as well as several different fonts you can choose from to style your content.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"?page_id=35\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n  \r\n<h2>Warp 6</h2>\r\n<p>Solar is based on the fast and slick Warp6 Theme Framework, which is built with the latest web techniques like HTML5, CSS3 and PHP 5.2+.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class=\"button-primary\" href=\"http://www.yootheme.com/themes/warp-framework\" target=\"_blank\">Continue Reading</a>\r\n','Responsive Layout','','publish','open','open','','responsive-layout','','','2013-01-09 11:01:47','2013-01-09 11:01:47','',0,'@@SITE_URL@@?p=674',0,'post','',0),(676,1,'2012-12-20 11:16:20','2012-12-20 11:16:20','<p>Solar is based o